com.codemelon.graph.vertex

Interface DfsVertex

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ColoredVertex, Vertex, VisitedVertex
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EdgeTypeDfsVertex<T>, OrderedDfsVertex
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectedDfsVertex, DirectedOrderedDfsVertex

    public interface DfsVertex
extends ColoredVertex, VisitedVertex
    Utility interface used as shorthand for vertices that implement ColoredVertex and VisitedVertex, as needed for the most basic kind of depth-first search.
